meta {
  name: Create SMS Template
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

post {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/templates
  body: json
  auth: bearer
}

headers {
  content-type: application/json
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{businessAccessToken}}
}

body:json {
  {
    "preference": "SMS",
    "feature": "lab_order_report_published_inform_patient",
    "displayTitle": "Report Ready Alert",
    "messageType": "TRANSACTIONAL",
    "isActive": true,
    "isDefault": false,
    "isEnabled": true,
    "level": "BUSINESS",
    "applicableBranchType": "LAB",
    "smsTemplateId": "1707161234567890123",
    "smsSenderId": "KALNOS",
    "smsType": "TRANSACTIONAL",
    "template": "Hi {patient_name}, your {test_name} report is ready: {report_link}"
  }
}

vars:pre-request {
  businessAccessToken: eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..J55wiEzB-FCqQGSFyaVmqeOfFIFJRrlK5d47mBUpMZ4
}

script:post-response {
  const data = res.getBody() && res.getBody().data;
  if (data && data.id) bru.setEnvVar("templateId", data.id);
}

docs {
  Create a messaging template in the caller's scope. Scope is derived from the
  JWT (`@CurrentProfile`): a **business_admin** token (`active_branch_id: null`)
  creates a **tenant-level** template; a **branch-admin** token creates a
  **branch-level** template for the active branch. `tenantId` / `branchId` are
  never sent in the body — they come from context. Captures `templateId`.

  ## Core fields (all channels)

  - `preference` (required): channel — `EMAIL` | `SMS` | `IAM` | `IAA` | `PBN` | `WHATSAPP` | `TEMPLATE`.
  - `feature` (required): one of the ~88 FEATURE_TYPES keys (see "Get Features").
  - `displayTitle` (optional): human-readable title (≤300 chars).
  - `messageType` (optional): `OTP` | `TRANSACTIONAL` | `MARKETING`.
  - `isActive` (optional, default `true`), `isDefault` (optional, default `false`), `isEnabled` (optional, default `false`).
  - `template` (required): body — rich HTML for `EMAIL`, else plain text with `{placeholders}` (≤20000 chars).

  ## Scope & targeting (optional)

  - `specificApplication`: `KALNOSTIC` (omit = all applications).
  - `applicableBranchType`: `LAB` | `CLINIC` | `HOSPITAL` | `BLOOD_BANK` | `RADIOLOGY` (omit = all).
  - `level`: `ADMIN` | `BUSINESS` (default `BUSINESS`).
  - `entityId` / `entityType`: free-text targeting values (≤45 chars each).

  ## SMS settings (SMS only)

  - `smsTemplateId`: DLT-registered SMS template id (≤255 chars).
  - `smsSenderId`: registered sender / header id, e.g. `KALNOS` (≤255 chars).
  - `smsType`: `TRANSACTIONAL` | `PROMOTIONAL`.
}
